{"tid":892171,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"萬七~八 Budget","createTime":"2018-11-06T16:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T01:54:19.000Z","uid":185943,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c3239fb4adac6aa7be40fbc9f831b7d060546a","tid":892171,"uid":185943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"用途: 多功, 主要繪圖3D, 畫圖<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">設計軟件都有機會用到</span>, 剪片(勁食cpu/次顯示卡同ram) <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔會打機</span></strong></span> <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">應該係</span></span><br />\n畫質隨意, 應該唔會超頻, 有冇RGB都冇所謂 ,唔想太熱(要耐用,怕死) ,以後唔會升件(所以牛夠用即可)<br />\n<br />\n自己屋企部野用開AMD多功 先萬一, 但AMD好似點砌都砌唔到萬七八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 砌部2080怕死太熱, 如果唔超應該點玩都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">因為唔係自己出錢</span>, <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以用盡佢</span></span> )  (我是但貼個機LIST好似多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n由於猶豫買MAC定WINDOW(實質budget兩萬, 如砌機要留兩千左右買雜野), 所以求解答邊樣岩用啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  隨便出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5d2daa393e37a87db75a695f0e7a1efc8d1612","tid":892171,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T23:03:53.000Z","msg":"用咩軟件剪片？"},{"pid":"655b7dbf53c930a39193f3247d0ab9c3e1f1bb2e","tid":892171,"uid":185943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c5d2daa393e37a87db75a695f0e7a1efc8d1612","tid":892171,"uid":58882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T23:03:53.000Z","msg":"用咩軟件剪片？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:08:07.000Z","msg":"adobe, 主要用3d多"},{"pid":"9f3d3212800d55f60cf375d8cbaf84426cc36d17","tid":892171,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2